    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "Your Email address",
        "subject": "=Daily Waste Saver Report — {{ $now.format('dd-MM-yyyy') }}",
        "message": "=<h2>🌿 Daily Waste Saver Combo Deals</h2>\n<p>Here are today's combo deals generated from near-expiry products:</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"8\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100%\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#e63946;color:white\">\n    <th>Combo Name</th>\n    <th>Products</th>\n    <th>Urgency</th>\n    <th>Discount</th>\n    <th>Final Price</th>\n    <th>Action</th>\n  </tr>\n  {{ $('Code in JavaScript1').all().map(item => `\n  <tr>\n    <td>${item.json['Combo Name']}</td>\n    <td>${item.json['Products']}</td>\n    <td>${item.json['Urgency']}</td>\n    <td>${item.json['Discount']}</td>\n    <td>${item.json['Final Price (DKK)']} DKK</td>\n    <td>${item.json['Action']}</td>\n  </tr>`).join('') }}\n</table>\n\n<p>The promotional flyer is attached to this email.</p>\n<p style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px\">This report was generated automatically by the WasteSaver system.\n<p>📎 <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/{{ $('Upload file').item.json.id }}/view\">Click here to view today's flyer</a></p>\n</p>",
        "options": {}
      },
